	dprr:hasNoteText "No title preserved. Author of a law to regulate money-lending (Fest. 268 L.; Non. Marc. 89 L; FOR 1.28 and 166). See Niccolini, FTP 400, who suggests a date in the period of Cato the Censor." ;
